Tyrael nods and starts glowing intensely. He transforms into a blue 
phoenix and starts flying in the air.

Tyrael: Come, Cygnar. There is quite a distance to travel from here.

He opens a channel with the base.

Tyrael: Cheetah, Tigerhawk, get ready for battle. I'm bringing some 
allies back with me, so don't start freaking out. Tyrael out.
